Pet Adoption Platform:

-Pet Adoption Company
        Data: List of Animals, address
        Behaviour: rescue animals
                   check customer background
                   give for adoption
                   cancel adoption
                   post new animals for adoption
                   charge Adoption Fee

-Animal
        Data: type, breed, age, sex, name, health, description, adoptionFee
        Behaviour:

-Customer
        Data: userID, address
        Behaviour: select animal
                   select breed
                   like animal
                   adopt animal
                   complete paper work
                   Pay adoption fee

PseudoCode:

Customer James;
Pet Adoption Company PetCo;

James.login(UserId,password);
Animal ginger = James.selectAnimal(AnimalType);
James.checkDescription(ginger);
if(James.likesAnimal)
James.fillPaperWork;
PetCo.checkBackground(James.fetchDetails);
    if(James.background is ok)
    James.payAdoptionFee(Credentials);
    PetCo.giveForAdoption(ginger,James);
    else if(James.Background is not ok)
    PetCo.cancelAdoption(James);
else
James.logout;







